{"tid":2447439,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國防部班美國豬原來咁驚中國","createTime":"2021-03-15T07:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T09:47:18.000Z","uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"589eee7dd6c06d6ad1738198d1be0adbc582875a","tid":2447439,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"美駐聯合國大使取消訪台內幕 中共警告尾隨專機犯台領空宣示主權<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/V6HX2P56SBGELFOCJO23WQFOIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2FV6HX2P56SBGELFOCJO23WQFOIQ%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDhOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=93262787\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2FV6HX2P56SBGELFOCJO23WQFOIQ%2F&h=9db5a07e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/V6HX2P56SBGELFOCJO23WQFOIQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣《新新聞》上周三（10日）引述消息人士指，拜登政府之所以對兩岸爭端持審慎態度，與美國前駐聯合國大使克拉夫特（Kelly Craft）計劃於今年1月訪台，幾乎引爆台海自1967年金門「113空戰」以來最接近開戰的危機有關。"},{"pid":"423af0a07a3f0ea33bc9dd4f74c2dc6da0d922da","tid":2447439,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"報道綜合兩岸軍情及外交人士的訊息指，從今年1月7日到10日，中方透過外交管道向美方強烈抗議不果後，北京高層最終決定以軍事行動回應；解放軍於11日透過中美兩軍聯繫機制告知美國國防部，無法容忍克拉夫特訪台損及中國主權利益，強調當美國專機抵達台灣附近時，解放軍戰機亦將會跟隨進入台灣領空，宣示台灣主權屬於中國的立場，而若過程中遭台灣軍機阻擋的話，不排除開火等後果"},{"pid":"8a53927d1e2c25a8cacaba4cb42c70cc56b2c4f9","tid":2447439,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:56:30.000Z","msg":"消息人士透露，當時美國國防部正忙於權力交接，未料到中方反應竟如此激烈，相關官員嘗試與解放軍高層溝通但被拒絕。經緊急通知，美軍印太司令部評估發現，若要保證克拉夫特專機安全降落台北，只有動用日本沖繩嘉手納空軍基地的空軍第18聯隊F15C戰機護航一途，但美中兩國空軍將有發生軍事對峙的風險；而即使改由台灣戰機全程護航，情況將更加棘手，一旦共軍戰機大舉跨越中線進逼，恐會與台灣戰機在北台灣空域引發戰火，屆時美國專機必須被迫轉降駐日美軍基地，「這樣一來美軍即使能置身事外，但放任兩岸引燃戰火對美國來說也會是一場政治大災難」。"},{"pid":"f2e28d5d0bb4efd8957ae833267bd0fd44aa2ea5","tid":2447439,"uid":188249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad92f25c4570f843a2993b9990243f67154a4839","tid":2447439,"uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"美國國防部及後將解放軍的警告，以及美軍相關評估結果告知國務院，並強烈建議克拉夫特取消訪台。蓬佩奧雖然對此非常不滿，但審慎考慮後果後亦同意取消，但為避免外界聯想克拉夫特訪台告吹是因為中國施壓奏效，才以政權交接為由一併取消所有官員的出訪計劃。<br />\n<br />\n美國豬咁都驚不如撤出東亞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6494374f63313eb126721382638d08634fb40b","tid":2447439,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:58:10.000Z","msg":"中國軍力已經超英趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e603c631e91dc95f0636eded0c2484cfa135382","tid":2447439,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"空有一身肌肉同武器  淆共匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d374d857b5e860a0b1566cfcd6d4f1ab3d62badf","tid":2447439,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"ATNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ab9ba0d16b0f4e82320dad3f19884fc6df983b","tid":2447439,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2e28d5d0bb4efd8957ae833267bd0fd44aa2ea5","tid":2447439,"uid":188249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"